text: Haji (Cerlet Catton; January 24, 1946 - August 10, 2013Haji, Star of Faster, Pussycat! Kill! Kill! Dead at 67 , laweekly.com, access date August 10, 2013) was a Canadian-born actress and former exotic dancer known for her role in the Russ Meyer's 1965 cult classic Faster, Pussycat! Kill! Kill!. Haji was born on January 24, 1946 in Quebec, Canada. She had one daughter out of wedlock.
